# Profile UI

## Objective
Create the character sheet view for the authenticated user.

## Tasks
1. Retrieve user profile data including XP and Level from Supabase.
2. Build a character sheet component displaying Level (e.g., Level 1), current XP, and unassigned Clan status.
3. Style with Tailwind CSS matching an RPG dark-fantasy/cypherpunk aesthetic.
